    public abstract class TomcatBaseTest
extends LoggingBaseTest
    Base test case that provides a Tomcat instance for each test - mainly so we don't have to keep writing the cleanup code.

      • getTomcatInstanceTestWebapp

        public Tomcat getTomcatInstanceTestWebapp(boolean addJstl,
                                          boolean start)
                                   throws LifecycleException
        Make the Tomcat instance preconfigured with test/webapp available to sub-classes.
        参数:
        addJstl - Should JSTL support be added to the test webapp
        start - Should the Tomcat instance be started
        返回:
        A Tomcat instance pre-configured with the web application located at test/webapp
        抛出:
        LifecycleException - If a problem occurs while starting the instance
